>> Intallation.
Installing Superalgos software went ahead without any major issues. However after running the software the web page appearance was unexpected. Many icons hear and there. Where do I start?
>>Tutorials
The welcome tutorial was quickly started. How does all of this work? 
Now at the beyond basics tutorial there is an inkling of realisation. There may be some order, some sense. Guess the tutorials need to be reviewed again and again for there is a clear understanding of the system.

To be updated
